title: GO Healthy
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Raw, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out
description: A smoothie & juice bar, a coffee shop and a healthy food store. You can find smoothies, juices, salads, sandwiches, toasts, paninis and wraps, some of which are vegan, as well as various seeds, nuts and packed healthy food. Also available is a variety of coffee with a choice of soy, almond and cashew milks.
